<center>

    <h1> Organized builds by categories.<br>
        Community driven. Community submitted.</h1>
    <h2>With your help of course.</h2>

    <h4>Collective builds was started to provide organized,<br>real build examples for those interest in building a PC.<br>
        Here you can find up to date, custom builds by the category of use.
        <br>If you have a great build to share, itâ€™s as easy as clicking the suggest a build.
